						               													<description>ARMOR UP!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In 3050, the true heirs of the lost Star League thunder forth from the depths of the far Periphery and carve deep into the quarreling Successor States. As the Clan juggernaut rolls across the coreward realms of the Inner Sphere, the House Lords scramble to shore up their defenses and devise some way to halt the invaders.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Clan spear is aimed at the heart of human-occupied space. Do you possess the bold tactics and heroic courage to defeat warriors trained from birth to conquer? Or will you uphold Kerensky&amp;rsquo;s dream to cast aside the squabbling lords of the Inner Sphere and reignite the flame of the Star League?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;BattleTech is the world&amp;rsquo;s greatest armored combat game, and now you can add the Clans! Inside this box you&amp;rsquo;ll discover epic clashes, dynamic characters, and a myriad of gaming experiences for any type of player: miniatures to RPG play, hobby painting to fiction, and beyond.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Clan Invasion includes everything you need to add Clans to your table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Battletech: Clan Invasion include the following items:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Battletech: Clan Invasion rulebook&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Battletech: Clan Invasion primer&amp;#10;&amp;bull; A 24 page Book of record sheets&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Battletech: Inner Sphere 3025/3052 double sided map&amp;#10;&amp;bull; A tables quick-reference card&amp;#10;&amp;bull; A sheet of cardboard punch outs including Mechs &amp;amp; Terrain Hexes&amp;#10;&amp;bull; The Bonds of Battle Novella&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Hilltops #1 mapsheet&amp;#10;&amp;bull; Rolling Hills #2 mapsheet&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 2 Six-sided dice&amp;#10;&amp;bull; A deck of pilot cards&amp;#10;&amp;bull; 7 High-quality miniatures (Grendel, Timberwolf, Executioner, Nove, Adder, 2 bases of Clan Elementals)&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
